          Your comprehensive guide to life in Switzerland's largest city. From housing to healthcare, discover everything you need to know about Zurich.
        </p>
        
        <!-- Quick Stats -->
        <div class="mt-10 grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-4">
          {quickStats.map((stat) => (
          <div class="bg-white/10 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-lg p-4">
            <dt class="text-gray-300 text-sm">{stat.label}</dt>
