        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Introduction Section -->
  <div class="bg-white py-16">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">Introduction to Zurich</h2>
        <div class="prose prose-lg">
        <p>
          Zurich, Switzerland's largest city and financial capital, consistently ranks among the world's most livable cities. With its stunning location on Lake Zurich, surrounded by the Alps, the city offers an exceptional quality of life, combining urban sophistication with natural beauty.
        </p>
        <p>
          Home to numerous multinational companies, leading universities, and a thriving startup scene, Zurich attracts professionals from around the globe. The city's efficient public transport, excellent healthcare system, and high standard of living make it particularly attractive to expats.
        </p>
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-8">Why Zurich is Attractive for Expats</h3>
        <ul>
          <li>
            <strong>High Quality of Life:</strong> Zurich consistently ranks high in global quality of life surveys, offering a safe, clean, and well-organized environment.
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>Economic Opportunities:</strong> As a major financial center, Zurich provides numerous job opportunities, particularly in finance, technology, and consulting.
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>Excellent Infrastructure:</strong> The city boasts a well-developed public transportation system, making it easy to get around.
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>Healthcare System:</strong> Zurich has a world-class healthcare system, though understanding insurance is crucial for expats.
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Living in Zurich -->
