                <h4 class="font-medium text-gray-900">Already Insured?</h4>
                <p class="text-gray-600 mt-1">Learn about <a href="/news/switching-health-insurance-in-switzerland" class="text-primary-600 hover:text-primary-800">switching health insurance providers</a> to get better rates.</p>
